cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.SE, cs.HC, cs.CY 

The paper discusses the use of artificial intelligence and machine learning in computer vision services, which falls under the categories of cs.AI and cs.CV. The evaluation of the responses of these services over time and the assessment of evolution risk falls under the category of cs.SE (software engineering). The lack of clear communication and documentation of risks and inconsistencies may also relate to human-computer interaction (cs.HC) and cybersecurity (cs.CY).
